reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These cubes make packing so much easier
reviews.reviewText: I made a trip to California this year with a group of people. Several had packing cubes which I had never seen. So when I got back home, I immediately purchased these in my favorite color. They are very light weight and sturdy. Packing is now very organized and easy to find what I need.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Light weight and sturdy cubes
reviews.reviewText: I have purchased several sets of packing cubes over the years but felt the zipper was flimsy and the sizes weren’t varied. This set has it all. They felt much sturdier out of the package. I liked the color (I ordered blue). The variation in size is also a plus.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent for an organized travel experience
reviews.reviewText: These cubes are a must have if you wish to have an organized travel experience. I ordered this product which arrived the very next day, no fuss no muss.
